name: Drawing-app
tagline: This is a simple drawing application built with jQuery.
body: ### Welcome to my Drawing App. This was practice with using jQuery to program my <canvas> with some cool functionality. Draw with pre-defined primary colors or create you own custom colors to play with! (Erase feature coming soon.) Thanks, for checking out my app.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
